{"tid":2307633,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–低卡路餐單對化療的影響","createTime":"2020-12-01T09:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:48:54.000Z","uid":38861,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe325c7d71cb75bdbbdc85dcd3670370c596319","tid":2307633,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"隨著針對癌細胞新陳代謝的研究逐漸倍增，配合飲食來醫治癌症這方面亦開始得到關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5ZqYP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5ZqYP0.jpg&h=9eb4c842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現今有不少利用實驗室細胞及動物的研究指出，低卡路里餐單能加強化療藥物醫治癌症的效果。科學家們對此曾提出不少理論試圖解釋這現象，但現今並沒有一道能獲取大部份人共識的理論。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有一項人體臨床研究找來129名乳癌病人（Ref1)，65人在療程中進食低卡路里餐單，而另外64人則沿用正常餐單。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsbXPWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsbXPWM.jpg&h=a03b3246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奈何因為味道及食慾等問題，最終只有22人能夠忍耐低卡路里餐單4星期，13人能夠忍耐8星期整個研究進程。<br />\n<br />\n正常餐單那方，亦有5名病人想在療程中途嘗試一下低卡路里餐單。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）圖中為低卡路里餐單的時間表。第一日攝取的總卡路里為1200，而之後的三日則為200卡路里，以碳水化合物為主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X48vqvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX48vqvg.png&h=bf1fcbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四日將會進行化療，而整個週期將重覆8次。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）文中並沒有列出正常餐單的成份，但從文中結果的血液各指標中可以看得到，低卡路里餐單的病人，血液酮體含量比正常餐單的病人為高，而胰島素含量則為低。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVtfBBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVtfBBY.png&h=a82d30f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這至少證明了低卡路里餐單的病人是一直處於「飢餓」的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）遵從低卡路里餐單的病人，化療3小時之後，某一組別的免疫細胞所受到的DNA傷害比正常餐單的人為低，為正面的良好效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Pnv9W1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Pnv9W1.png&h=f3f494cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但低卡路里餐單能否使化療效果事半功倍，還需要更多的病人數量才能得出結論。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，開發出能夠讓病人廣泛接受的低卡路里餐單，亦是一道需要關注的問題。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0reFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=7c6808cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-16138-3#Sec20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41467-020-16138-3%23Sec20&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0reFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=bf3300f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-16138-3#Sec20</a>"},{"pid":"7d9120ff2bd10e1b5748e286fa318c9ddd50c5cf","tid":2307633,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3b2b659a13efc8296e38fe37f775659b1c41b2","tid":2307633,"uid":155238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲 cancer patient睇落已經營養不良咁款㗎啦，仲要低卡路里餐單會唔會死人㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eca3313a214edda04fe4af2f6a19d7c6e572f1","tid":2307633,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b2b659a13efc8296e38fe37f775659b1c41b2","tid":2307633,"uid":155238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲 cancer patient睇落已經營養不良咁款㗎啦，仲要低卡路里餐單會唔會死人㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"睇落去似營養不良啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7e2c5899bbeff92cb72a81a19e951ab7112293","tid":2307633,"uid":38861,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b2b659a13efc8296e38fe37f775659b1c41b2","tid":2307633,"uid":155238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲 cancer patient睇落已經營養不良咁款㗎啦，仲要低卡路里餐單會唔會死人㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實依方面仲有好多爭論，雖然低卡路里（間隔斷食）有好多證據指出可以令化療加強成效，但又有好多證據顯示癌細胞會不斷消耗肌肉來獲取蛋白質，如果喺依個情況下仲斷食，究竟會唔會惡化肌肉被侵蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時間，主流顯示脂肪酸有助防止癌細胞從原本位置轉移到另一位置，患癌究竟應該點進食真係好難決擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbde53fab18cb6bd96e89790acfbc7fca2cb5d41","tid":2307633,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1694d66f8693046dd7c84018a770b7b7266c0d16","tid":2307633,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b2b659a13efc8296e38fe37f775659b1c41b2","tid":2307633,"uid":155238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲 cancer patient睇落已經營養不良咁款㗎啦，仲要低卡路里餐單會唔會死人㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"將來應該都要研究<br />\n等個主題都未研究完點會走去做呢啲嘢"},{"pid":"ac3259f1c8520ab2511fca6e4ff391eb1a1a5100","tid":2307633,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1694d66f8693046dd7c84018a770b7b7266c0d16","tid":2307633,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b2b659a13efc8296e38fe37f775659b1c41b2","tid":2307633,"uid":155238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲 cancer patient睇落已經營養不良咁款㗎啦，仲要低卡路里餐單會唔會死人㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"將來應該都要研究<br />\n等個主題都未研究完點會走去做呢啲嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyT